IonoObservationStokes_Ingest.description: /// Multi-dimensional array with the same dimensions as power plus one additional dimension spanning an S dimension for S1, S2, and S3 (the normalized Stokes parameters 1, 2, and 3). It is advised to describe the antenna type, antenna configuration, and Stokes coordinate system as a notes to the variable.

notes.description:
Notes for the stokes data.
Example: /// Example: NOTES
Constraints: Minimum length = 0, Maximum length = 512

dimensions.description:
Array of integers of the stoke array dimensions.
Example: /// Example: [2, 3]
Constraints: No constraints specified.

dimensionName.description:
Array of names for dimensions.
Example: /// Example: ['NAMES1', 'NAMES2']
Constraints: No constraints specified.

data.description:
Array of received stokes data.
Example: /// Example: [[[[[[[0.02, 0.034]]]]]]]
Constraints: No constraints specified.

s.description:
S1, S2, and S3 (the normalized Stokes parameters 1, 2, and 3).
Example: /// Example: [1.0, 2.0]
Constraints: No constraints specified.
